OL,3,CUp to 450 jobs at risk at Somerset
OL,4,CCouncil
OL,6,FAs many as 450 jobs could be cut at
OL,7,FSomerset Council as the local
OL,8,Fauthority looks to make savings.
OL,10,FA consultation on the redundancies has
OL,11,Fbeen launched, and will last 45 days.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Somerset Council
OL,14,Fsaid it has already reduced the number
OL,15,Fof Executive Directors and Service
OL,16,FDirectors saving #1.5m, but added that
OL,17,Ffurther redundancies are likely.
OL,19,FA "worst-case scenario" would see 450
OL,20,Ffull-time roles made redundant by
OL,21,FApril 2025.
