OL,3,CUp to 450 jobs at risk at Somerset
OL,4,CCouncil
OL,6,FIt comes as the local authority is
OL,7,Flooking to make savings of up to #40m
OL,8,Fto avoid going bust.
OL,10,FA statement issued by Somerset Council
OL,11,Freads: "In response to the financial
OL,12,Femergency, we previously agreed to a
OL,13,Ftop-to-bottom restructure of the whole
OL,14,Fcouncil to save #30-#40m by April 2025
OL,15,Fto contribute to balancing the budget
OL,16,Ffor 2025/26, in addition to
OL,17,Fsignificant savings already made.
OL,19,F"We are now consulting with Trade
OL,20,FUnions and staff before any final
OL,21,Fdecisions are made.
