OL,6,F"While the size of the workforce will
OL,7,Freduce, we will continue to protect
OL,8,Fand provide essential services for our
OL,9,Fresidents, communities and businesses,
OL,10,Fwhile continuing to lobby government
OL,11,Ffor fairer funding.
OL,13,F"Restructuring will help to create
OL,14,Ffuture organisational and financial
OL,15,Fstability while providing clarity for
OL,16,Fstaff on the future Council structure
OL,17,Fand roles, and ensure we have an
OL,18,Faffordable staffing budget from April
OL,19,F2025."
